    "correct": 0,
    "explanation": "Let's calculate the water consumption day by day, including the spills and extra water due to exercise.\n\n**Monday (20-ounce bottle, 3 refills, 5 ounces spilled):**\n- Total consumed: 3 refills * 20 ounces = 60 ounces\n- Spilled: 5 ounces\n- Actual consumption: 60 ounces - 5 ounces = 55 ounces\n\n**Tuesday (32-ounce bottle, 2 refills, extra 20 ounces for exercise):**\n- Total consumed: 2 refills * 32 ounces = 64 ounces\n- Extra for exercise: 20 ounces\n- Actual consumption: 64 ounces + 20 ounces = 84 ounces\n\n**Wednesday (20-ounce bottle, 3 refills):**\n- Total consumed: 3 refills * 20 ounces = 60 ounces\n- Actual consumption: 60 ounces (no spill)\n\n**Thursday (32-ounce bottle, 2 refills, 8 ounces spilled, extra 20 ounces for exercise):**\n- Total consumed: 2 refills * 32 ounces = 64 ounces\n- Spilled: 8 ounces\n- Extra for exercise: 20 ounces\n- Actual consumption: 64 ounces - 8 ounces + 20 ounces = 76 ounces\n\n**Friday (20-ounce bottle, 3 refills):**\n- Total consumed: 3 refills * 20 ounces = 60 ounces\n- Actual consumption: 60 ounces (no spill)\n\n**Saturday (32-ounce bottle, 2 refills, extra 32 ounces for exercise):**\n- Total consumed: 2 refills * 32 ounces = 64 ounces\n- Extra for exercise: 32 ounces\n- Actual consumption: 64 ounces + 32 ounces = 96 ounces\n\n**Sunday (20-ounce bottle, 2 refills, 32-ounce bottle, 1 refill, 3 ounces spilled):**\n- Total consumed from 20-ounce bottle: 2 refills * 20 ounces = 40 ounces\n- Total consumed from 32-ounce bottle: 1 refill * 32 ounces = 32 ounces\n- Spilled: 3 ounces\n- Actual consumption: (40 ounces + 32 ounces) - 3 ounces = 72 ounces - 3 ounces = 69 ounces\n\nNow, let's add up the actual consumption for each day to get the total for the week:\n\n55 ounces (Monday) + 84 ounces (Tuesday) + 60 ounces (Wednesday) + 76 ounces (Thursday) + 60 ounces (Friday) + 96 ounces (Saturday) + 69 ounces (Sunday)\n\nTotal consumption for the week = 55 + 84 + 60 + 76 + 60 + 96 + 69 = 500 ounces\n\nTherefore, Remi drinks a total of 500 ounces of water in 7 days.",
