    "question": "Given the following system of equations:\n\n1) f(x) = x^4 - 5x^3 + ax^2 + bx + c\n2) g(x) = -2x^5 + 7x^4 - 3x^3 - x^2 + dx + e\n3) h(x) = x^6 + 2x^5 - 4x^4 + 3x^3 - 2x^2 + fx + g\n\nWith the conditions:\n\nf(-1) = g(2), g(-1) = h(2), and h(-2) = f(1)\n\nDetermine the coefficients a, b, c, d, e, f, and g.\n\n### Answer:",
